      <title>歐盟結束在自由派圖斯克領導下針對波蘭的法治訴訟</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/eu-ends-rule-of-law-proceedings-against-poland-2024-05-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[歐盟委員會主席烏蘇拉·馮德萊恩週一表示，歐盟委員會將結束針對波蘭長達六年的法治訴訟，這標誌著該國開啟了「新篇章」。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/eu-ends-rule-of-law-proceedings-against-poland-2024-05-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 10:26:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
