      <title>馬賽垃圾收集者在奧運火炬抵達前罷工</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/marseille-garbage-collectors-strike-ahead-olympic-torch-arrival-2024-05-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[馬賽公共管理部門週日要求當地國家當局徵用罷工的垃圾收集工人，迫使足夠多的人重返工作崗位以維持服務，預計奧運火炬將在兩天前到達港口城市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/marseille-garbage-collectors-strike-ahead-olympic-torch-arrival-2024-05-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 09:22:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
